README.txt

All files contained in Stage 4 folder

Description:
Airline System that manages certain tasks such as passengers, booking, etc.
Make sure you have all source files.

Prerequisites.
JVM (Java Virtual Machine)
A java compiler
A terminal, command prompt, or interface

Running Instructions without IDE:
1. Open the Command Prompt in the location that the .java files are stored or pathfind these files.
2. Use this command in the promt, java -jar "AirlineManagementSystem.jar" 
